line_1: Slave to the tribe, to whose command she stoops,
line_2: And poorer than the poorest maid she dupes.

line_1: Where o'er the mead the mountain stoops,
line_2: Her cave the mining coney scoops;

line_1: If prest by Grief our Monarch stoops;
line_2: If He, whose Hand sustain'd them, droops;

line_1: While prest by Grief their MONARCH stoops;
line_2: If He, whose Hand sustain'd them, droops:
